		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>Your form shimmers as you send a wave of psionic energy washing over your foes. In their minds, you fade away as your duplicate appears and threatens them.</i></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Daily âœ¦ Conjuration, Illusion, Psionic</b></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Minor Action</b><b> &#8226; </b><b>Ranged</b> 5</p><p><b>Effect:</b> You conjure an illusory duplicate of yourself in an unoccupied square within range. The duplicate lasts until the end of the encounter. You gain a +4 power bonus to all defenses against any attack that doesn't include both you and the duplicate. As part of a move action, you can move the duplicate 5 squares. </p><p>The duplicate can be targeted by melee attacks and ranged attacks, although it lacks hit points. The duplicate disappears if a melee or a ranged attack deals any damage to it. </p><p>Published in Player's Handbook 3, page(s) 50. </p>",
